casebody.data:
M.S., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4858 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 4, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Because M.S. has failed to file and serve an initial brief as provided by this court's orders of March 5, 2018, and April 11, 2018, this appeal is dismissed for failure to prosecute.

CASANUEVA, ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, and ATKINSON, JJ., Concur.
